isPublic.label: Ruum armej
isPublic.description: Ruum ko an armej remaroñ pukot jān rijerbal ro jet .

allowGuestJoin.label: Kwōn kōtļo̧k an ri-lotok ro kobatok .
allowGuestJoin.description: Kōtļo̧k bwe rijerbal ro rejjab rentāer ren kobaļo̧k ilo ruum̧ eo āinwōt juon rilotok .

isEncrypted.label: Ej maroñ jeṃḷọk tōprak .
isEncrypted.description: N̄e ej kōtļo̧k, ennaan ko ilo ruum̧ eo renaaj bōk jikin jemļo̧k-n̄an-jem̧ļo̧k .
isEncrypted.alert: Ej juon menin aikuj bwe jen lale wāween an jet armej ļōmņak kōn jet armej.

form.submit: Ej kōjparok wāween ko n̄an kōjparok

toast.success: Eṃōj kōkāāl wāween ko ñan kōṃṃan jerbal .
toast.error: Ejjab maroñ kōkāāl wāween ko an armej .
